title: Pop On In! Beautiful 2 Bed 2 Bath, Tour Today!
posting_body: ['23425 Southeast Black Nugget Road, Issaquah, WA 98029', 'The Timbers at Issaquah Ridge offers virtual and self-guided tours as well as online leasing!', '\xa0Take a tour\xa0and\xa0rent an apartment\xa0without leaving your couch.', 'The Timbers at Issaquah Ridge is a premier apartment community situated amongst\xa0beautiful scenery in the heart of Issaquah.', '\xa0Community amenities include an upgraded resident lounge, media room, theater, playground and Wi-Fi lounge.', 'Our\xa0homes\xa0feature generous sized flats\xa0and townhomes with upgraded interiors, large windows that provide gorgeous mountain views and private patios or balconies.', '\xa0Choose from our one-, two-, three- and four-bedroom\xa0layouts\xa0for a home that is just minutes to the\xa0Microsoft Connector and\xa0Amazon Ride bus stops.', '\xa0Contact us\xa0for additional details about our preferred employer discounts!', 'Community Features:', 'Dog Park', 'Media Room', 'Attached Garage', 'Fitness Center', 'Clubhouse', '24/7 Emergency Maintenance', 'Business Center', 'Carports', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Townhomes Issaquah - The Timbers at Issaquah Ridge, Issaquah Highlands Apartments - The Timbers at Issaquah Ridge, Apartments in Issaquah Highlands - The Timbers at Issaquah Ridge, Find apartments for rent in Issaquah. , Stunning Issaquah Apartments for rent.', '*Floor plans and pricing are subject to error, change or deletion.', 'Some photos are for representation purposes only.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
